    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "As much as this is better than bleed, the keys are still crap.\nR does nothing, infantry are on T. While this may be OK for other mods, it's not for D2k.\nAnd after that the tabs go: Vehicles, Tanks, Aircraft, Starport; but the hotkeys go Vehicles, Aircraft, Tanks, Starport.\nI get why all this is happening, but I'd rather have them non-configurable, if that means we can hardcode the proper keys.\n\nP.S.: I vote we hardcode proper hotkeys (E, R, T, Y, U, I) for D2k while the issue I just opened for per-mod hotkey configurations gets implemented and then we can do this properly.\n"
